* Data Source\nConnections
** Authentication
***_ Secrets (Databricks secrets vault)
***_ Service principals
***_ OAuth / API keys
** Network Connectivity
***_ VNet peering / Private endpoints
***_ ExpressRoute / VPN for on-prem
***_ Firewall rules
** Source System Impact
***_ Throttling to avoid overload
***_ Scheduling during off-peak
***_ Read-only access recommended
@endmindmap
